data.description: Three bed, two and a half bath end unit near Dam Neck and Oceana Naval Bases. This charming two story townhouse features an open floor plan, spacious eat-in kitchen with stainless appliances and wood burning fireplace. The fenced in backyard offers a private deck with a view of the pond. The upstairs includes a large en suite, two more bedrooms, a second full bath and a separate laundry room. Great location near beaches, restaurants and shopping!
